Description: # langswi
        
        Keyboard layout switcher for cyrillic-latin & reversed symbols.
        
        ## First of all
        
        Install the package:
        
        ```
        pip install langswi
        ```
        
        When layout will be missed, just copy text into the buffer and type: 
        
        ```
        langswi
        ```
        
        ![Subway Scheme](demo.gif)
        
        ## That's it.
        
